#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.gammaln.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.special.gammaln"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammaln:1 of
msgid "Logarithm of the absolute value of the Gamma function."
msgstr "伽马函数绝对值的对数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammaln of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammaln:3 of
msgid "Values on the real line at which to compute ``gammaln``"
msgstr "用于计算 ``gammaln`` 的实数轴上的值"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammaln:5 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须可以广播到输入的形状。如果未提供"
"或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（仅可作为关键字参数）的长度必须"
"等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammaln:10 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammaln of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammaln:15 of
msgid "**gammaln** -- Values of ``gammaln`` at x."
msgstr "**gammaln** -- x 处的 ``gammaln`` 值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammaln of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammaln:20 of
msgid ":py:obj:`gammasgn`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammaln:21 of
msgid "sign of the gamma function"
msgstr "伽马函数的符号"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammaln:23 of
msgid ":py:obj:`loggamma`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammaln:24 of
msgid "principal branch of the logarithm of the gamma function"
msgstr "伽马函数对数的主分支"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammaln:27 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammaln:28 of
msgid ""
"When used in conjunction with `gammasgn`, this function is useful for "
"working in logspace on the real axis without having to deal with complex "
"numbers, via the relation ``exp(gammaln(x)) = gammasgn(x)*gamma(x)``."
msgstr ""
"与 `gammasgn` 结合使用时，此函数通过关系式 ``exp(gammaln(x)) = gammasgn(x"
")*gamma(x)``，可以在实轴上以对数空间进行计算，而无需处理复数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammaln:32 of
msgid "For complex-valued log-gamma, use `loggamma` instead of `gammaln`."
msgstr "对于复数值的对数伽马函数，请使用 `loggamma` 而不是 `gammaln`。"

